<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="apology-n">apology <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'pɒlədʒi/    美 /ə'pɑːlədʒi/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>道歉；歉意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>accept sb’s apology</strong>
接受某人的道歉</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>owe sb an apology</strong>
应该向某人道歉</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>demand</strong> an immediate <strong>apology</strong> from you.
我要求你立即道歉。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I must <strong>make an apology to</strong> him <strong>for</strong> not going to his party.
没有参加他的聚会，我得向他道歉。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— Go and say sorry to your Mom, Dave.
— I’d like to, but I’m afraid she won’t be happy with my  <strong><em>_</em></strong>_.  （2015 江苏）<br />
A.requests<br />
B.excuses<br />
C.apologies<br />
D.regrets  </li>
<li>I have an <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (道歉) to make to you — I’m afraid I opened your letter by mistake.   （2011 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. C  2. apology  </p></div>